race.comment: WITHOUT ME (1) turned in a solid run last start over 300m at this track finishing 5th and beaten only 5 lengths (17.97). Should be very hard to beat this time. MUM'S ON FIRE (2) missed the frame and safely held latest finishing 6th at this track following on from a win (17.92) there the start prior. Can do much better this time. ROCKY BELL (8) is worth forgiving last start after finishing fifth (18.09) from Box 7 at this track over 300m. Great chance to atone. IMPRESS BEV (7) can finish much closer after missing a cheque at this track last start.
